@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h1 class="card-title mb-3">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
                    <p class="text-muted">Last updated: April 8, 2025</p>

                    <p>At <strong>eTutoring</strong>, we are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your personal data with care. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when using our platform.</p>

                    <h4 class="mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3">
                        <li class="list-group-item">Personal Info: name, date of birth, email, phone, address, profile photo, encrypted credentials.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">Usage Data: login history, course activity, lesson interaction, feedback.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">Payment Info: methods, transactions, invoices (for learners).</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3">
                        <li class="list-group-item">Manage user accounts (learners & tutors)</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">Match learners with suitable tutors</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">Track learning progress</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">Provide customer support</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">Improve platform features</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4>3. Information Sharing</h4>
                    <p>We <strong>do not sell or share</strong> your personal information except in the following cases:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>With your explicit consent</li>
                        <li>When required by law or authorities</li>
                        <li>With payment processors (only necessary data)</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4>4. Data Security</h4>
                    <p>We implement robust measures to protect your data:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Encrypted passwords</li>
                        <li>HTTPS secured connection</li>
                        <li>Role-based access control</li>
                        <li>Regular backups & security audits</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4>5. Your Rights</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Access, update or delete your information</li>
                        <li>Close account and request data deletion</li>
                        <li>Withdraw previously granted permissions</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4>6. Cookies & Tracking</h4>
                    <p>We use cookies to enhance performance and remember your preferences. You may disable them in your browser settings, but this might affect functionality.</p>

                    <h4>7. Data Retention</h4>
                    <p>Your data is kept as long as your account is active. Upon deletion, it will be anonymized or removed within <strong>30 days</strong>.</p>

                    <h4>8. Policy Updates</h4>
                    <p>We may update this policy. Changes will be notified via email or within the platform.</p>

                    <h4>9. Contact Us</h4>
                    <p>If you have any questions regarding this policy:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Email:</strong> support@etutoring.vn</li>
                        <li><strong>Hotline:</strong> 1900 1234</li>
                        <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://etutoring.vn" target="_blank">etutoring.vn</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
